&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong base salary. We offer competitive pay that reflects your skills and experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexible work location. Enjoy the freedom to work from home or from the office.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Remote work. Spend up to 30 days per year working remotely from abroad.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Extra time off. More days to relax, recharge, and do the things you love.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Medical insurance allowance. Enjoy peace of mind for you and your family&lt;/li&gt;
