&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About JetBrains&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At JetBrains, code is our passion. Ever since we started, back in 2000, we have been striving to make the strongest, most effective developer tools on earth. Over 15.9 million developers already use our products, and 88 Fortune Global Top 100 companies are JetBrains customers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
