&lt;li&gt;Have at least five years of customer-facing experience in sales engineering, solutions engineering, customer success engineering, or a similar customer-facing field.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Possess strong interpersonal communication skills, both verbal and written – you will need to speak and write English fluently, as it is the preferred language of communication with our customers and partners, as well as within the team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have ​experience in driving discussions with both technical and non-technical audiences.&lt;/li&gt;
